    "body": "When loading `openpmd-api` as a lib to build outside of spack or to build depending spack packages, the \"CMake-PUBLIC\" header-only library MPark.Variant must be available. Also, the `*Config.cmake` package must be able to find dependent libs if used.\r\n\r\nMore details in #2378. Avoids to always require `spack load -r openpmd-api`.",
